    "We evaluate the three types of analysis described above on the task for predicting the success of Kickstarter crowdfunding campaigns in terms of the amount of money raised.",
    "We focus on crowdfunding campaigns that are concerned with 3D printing.",
    "On the one hand, this technology is currently in the state of fast growth, with its broad adoption seen across many industry sectors.",
    "On the other hand, this narrow technical domain presents itself as a suitable case study, where model interpretation can uncover specific, previously unknown insights.",
    "Experimental data for the study was collected from Kickstarter, one of the oldest and most popular reward-based crowd-funding platforms (Frydrych et al., 2014)."
